{"tid":2281371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老婆啊 唔好嬲我啦好無啊 我真係好愛你㗎","createTime":"2020-11-11T06:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T17:37:28.000Z","uid":431,"like":15,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"4027656aad1030646fd43c6ed16b924f4d40b516","tid":2281371,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"我唔想同你分開啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一直以嚟都好想全世界都知道你係我㗎...<br />\n我唔想同你分開啊 我知我有時講嘅嘢真係好難聽好唔合理 但我真係好愛你㗎...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好愛你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你平時叫我唔好喊 我無喊 我咪改囉...<br />\n我淨係唔想無咗你咋... 點解要分開啊......<br />\n我寧願死我都唔想無咗你啊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02caaa10d3207b2ba20af2ab782bbd57c012a034","tid":2281371,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:58:27.000Z","msg":"點解你要同我講分開啊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊咗年幾喇... 點解要就嚟結婚你先咁講啊？<br />\n我個心真係好痛啊......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你啦唔好分開得唔得啊...<br />\n我唔想無咗你啊... 俾我照顧你啦好無啊？<br />\n唔好唔好啦... 唔好唔要我得唔得啊.... 我想同你生存落去啊！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458844e8927a26d17738a7a9d33bc66b62f6047a","tid":2281371,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:58:55.000Z","msg":"我知我有時講嘢真係好難聽啊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我改啊我咩都肯改啊..<br />\n我淨係唔想無咗你咋.... 我唔想分開啊...<br />\n由我戴隻戒子嗰日開始我就無諗過同你分開...<br />\n我依家要話畀全世界人聽我真係好愛你啊<br />\n我唔想無咗你啊.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你啦 你同我唔係唔夾啊... 而係大家脾氣臭...<br />\n咪大家忍下囉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一直以嚟我知自己做咗好多嘢啊....<br />\n你返嚟我身邊啦好無啊？我無咗你真係唔知可以做啲咩啊.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知我無用... <br />\n男人喊咩啊... 我唔想㗎...<br />\n我心好痛啊你知唔知啊.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e071c82db40363cfa348965562d0c1e3d00006","tid":2281371,"uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"我同你去過好多地方 我之前應承過你要送一份禮物畀你我一直都無做到...<br />\n求下你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾我做埋依件事得唔得啊？？？<br />\n我送埋依件禮物畀你先分開好無啊？？？？<br />\n我唔想無咗你啊... 老婆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有半年我哋就可以結婚喇...<br />\n點解依家先要分手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個心真係好痛啊..........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e96109e792af82a7a45e4816e1e27bf7598a42a","tid":2281371,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:59:38.000Z","msg":"我唔知仲可以挨幾耐啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一直都好珍惜你....<br />\n每一次你唔開心我就攬住你... 我依家好想你攬住我啊...<br />\n老婆啊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我求下你返嚟我身邊好無啊？唔好再嬲我啦<br />\n我真係知錯喇...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家淨係想聽到你把聲我想你打畀我啊...<br />\n打畀我啦好無啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好掛住你啊....<br />\n真係好掛住你啊.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知我咩都無為你做過 我無用啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去旅行幾時去都得啊.... 我咩都唔要啊...<br />\n我淨係想你唔好同我分開咋 唔想無咗你啊...<br />\n求下你啦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好同我分開啦...<br />\n我個心好似俾人刀割咁好痛啊....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f168f113b888983d2dd2871a47a4a0f99b1ff8","tid":2281371,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"老婆啊... 畀次機會我啊........<br />\n畀我照顧你一生一世好唔好啊...<br />\n我唔會再講難聽嘅嘢㗎喇... 求下你啦............<br />\n畀次機會我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />畀我做你心目中嘅男人得唔得？<br />\n你喺我心目中嚟講好重要... 我真係好愛你㗎......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34301ab69f53aaa431855ac27ad8b3844c801411","tid":2281371,"uid":376562,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:00:05.000Z","msg":"因咩事先?"},{"pid":"feb09a357d5c340f5b6733fa434696c5228f21aa","tid":2281371,"uid":258784,"like":13,"dislike":5,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:00:13.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">感 建 分</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p>"},{"pid":"8e5687f6230c7e74e0db7da3dee622a5b863484d","tid":2281371,"uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:00:43.000Z","msg":"你平時要我喺街大聲咁同你講我愛你... 我唔係唔講啊<br />\n我唔係怕醜啊.... 而係我想知道我就算我講咗你係咪以後都唔會離開我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔知要點樣𠱁你<br />\n你要我喺街跳舞你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係我想跳畀你一個人睇咋！！<br />\n我愛你唔係講出聲㗎... 係擺個心入面㗎.........<br />\n一直以嚟我都對你好信任<br />\n我成日問你點解你唔打畀我點解唔搵我點解咁耐先搵我<br />\n唔係我唔信你去搵第2個而係我太著緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想失去你啊你明唔明啊？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97be7d2a8ce5aba82b7cc06f5ded42ae0d1c243b","tid":2281371,"uid":325757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又扮share ac"},{"pid":"ecfc43092e9b38605f5729bb48ee155a93531593","tid":2281371,"uid":162930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a79f2bea46a5e262e8ba937b5c019d9a